      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2018 executive sedan is a prime example of a well-maintained luxury vehicle that is ready for its next chapter. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Metallic Graphite that still holds a deep, impressive shine; while there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel rim, the body is straight and free of any major dents. Inside, the cabin has been kept in excellent shape. The premium leather upholstery is soft and intact, showing only light bolstering wear on the driver\u2019s seat. All interior electronics, from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent oil change and brake inspection performed just last month. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts without hesitation, and the suspension remains tight and quiet over bumps. This is a non-smoker vehicle with a clean title, offering a reliable and upscale driving experience for a discerning buyer.",
